They had a lot of fun, and it took a lot of the winter blues out of their minds  Regretably Beans and Lew had to step down Emily just fell in love with the swan that beans posted. Something a little sedemendal to her ,a story for another day.   Well  Here you go Folks  The Winner is   Drums rolling   Congrats

On a sad note Beans and Lew had to drop out My youngest was firm on the swan pic.  A special thanks goes out to the boss,T J and all the mods for allowing me to do this.
